<body>
    <h1>zones/zonegroup</h1>

        <p>These events are to do with the control/feedback of a zone group.</p>

    <h2>General</h2>

        <p>A zone group is responsible for control of anything that is used by multiple zones.</p> 

    <h3>http://id.webbrick.co.uk/zones/zonegroup</h3>
        <p>This is the event type for all events to do with the zone group.</p>

    <h3>zonegroup/n/run</h3>
        <p>This event source indicates a requirement to run any devices required by the zone group n.</p>

    <h3>zonegroup/n/stop</h3>
        <p>This event source indicates there is now no requirement to run any devices required by the zone group n.</p>

    <h3>zonegroup/n/running</h3>
        <p>This event source indicates that the zone group n is running.</p>

    <h3>zonegroup/n/stopped</h3>
        <p>This event source indicates the zone group n has stopped.</p>
</body>

